00:00:00.490 --> 00:00:04.000
&gt;&gt; So, how will this course help you become a design-minded developer?

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.380
&gt;&gt; Well, we're going to go through four lessons.

00:00:06.380 --> 00:00:08.760
The first lesson is what is UX? We're going to

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:11.080
learn about the difference between UI and UX,

00:00:11.080 --> 00:00:13.300
because there's a lot of misinformation out there. The

00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:16.500
second lesson is about how to create applications

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:18.810
for specific users. And we're going to use tools called

00:00:18.810 --> 00:00:22.350
personas and use cases. The third lesson is

00:00:22.350 --> 00:00:25.510
about mobile design constraints. Because after all, this course

00:00:25.510 --> 00:00:28.150
is for mobile developers. And in lesson

00:00:28.150 --> 00:00:29.880
four, you're going to learn how to leverage

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:31.950
the power of the Android platform to

00:00:31.950 --> 00:00:34.890
