00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:41.010
an opportunity to put into practice at the end

00:00:41.010 --> 00:00:42.780
of every lesson, in the form of an assignment.

00:00:42.780 --> 00:00:44.500
&gt;&gt; And the assignments are going to be

00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:47.730
led by a Udacity course designer named Andy.

